{{十干十二支|qq=}} '''Wu''' (戊, bo, tsuchinoe) is the 5th of the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|8=en|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. <ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=a602092fc003df5c0e16c71ef5b5a2fa1b5c015d65d986c106e397da1aa7e8afJmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Tsuchinoe+(%e6%88%8a)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGFub3NoaWlqYXBhbmVzZS5jb20vZGljdGlvbmFyeS9lbnRyeV9kZXRhaWxzLmNmbT9lbnRyeV9pZD01NjM0NA&ntb=1</ref><ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=b0de9cef7fbb919ba00edd65e5b6b759ce4515543c9394cfdbaa7bbe5e0c409cJmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Tsuchinoe+(%e6%88%8a)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmlob25nb21hc3Rlci5jb20vamFwYW5lc2UvZGljdGlvbmFyeS93b3JkLzU2MTkwL3RzdWNoaW5vZS1iby0lRTYlODglOEEtJUUzJTgxJUE0JUUzJTgxJUExJUUzJTgxJUFFJUUzJTgxJTg4LSVFMyU4MSVCQw&ntb=1</ref><ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=36c3b523c25f60637ea315b490ada1cd1c95eca16de8466a448a1c65722068a6JmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Tsuchinoe+(%e6%88%8a)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9qbGVhcm4ubmV0L2RpY3Rpb25hcnkvJUU2JTg4JThB&ntb=1</ref>
It is different from the character [https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E6%88%89 戉].
== Overview == * In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Five Elements theory|ja|陰陽五行説|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, Wu is associated with the yang aspect of the element {{ill|Earth (element)|ja|土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In Japan, it is also called "{{ill|Tsuchinoe|ja|つちのえ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}" (Elder Brother of Earth). * In terms of direction, it corresponds to the {{ill|Center|ja|中央|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. Regarding time, it refers to around 4 a.m., with the period from 4 a.m. to 6 a.m. known as "{{ill|Boya|ja|戊夜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}." * The character "戊" is an {{ill|ideogram|ja|象形文字|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} representing a weapon resembling a battle-axe.<ref>{{Citation| author=Ji Xusheng| year=2014| title=Shuowen Xinzheng| location=Taipei| publisher=Yiwen Press| isbn=978-957-520-168-5| pages=962–93|qq=}}</ref><ref>{{Citation| author=Ge Liang| year=2022| title=Rediscovery of Chinese Characters| location=Shanghai| publisher=Shanghai Calligraphy and Painting Press| isbn=978-7-5479-2884-4| pages=102–105|qq=}}</ref> Its use to denote the fifth of the Ten Heavenly Stems is a case of {{ill|Jiajie|ja|仮借|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (phonetic loan). * When used in ordinal contexts, Wu represents the 5th position. * Years ending with the digit 8 in the {{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are designated as Wu years. Another name for the Wu year is "{{ill|Zhuoyong|ja|著雍|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}" (also written as "{{ill|著雝|ja|著雝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}").<ref>{{Cite web |title=Ancient Alternative Names and Explanations of Heavenly Stems and Earthly Branches |url=https://www.cidianwang.com/shufazuopin/jiaocheng/932596.htm |website=www.cidianwang.com |access-date=2024-03-08|qq=}}</ref> * In {{ill|Chinese chemical nomenclature|ja|化合物命名法|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, it is used in the names of compounds containing five carbon atoms, such as {{ill|Pentane|ja|ペンタン|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and the {{ill|Pentyl group|ja|ペンチル基|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. * Its counterpart is {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Mizunoto). * The {{ill|Lucky direction|ja|恵方|3=歳徳神|1=Toshitoku-shin|lt=Lucky direction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} associated with Wu is south-southeast, slightly south (165 degrees). ==Sexagenary cycles containing Tsuchinoe (戊)==
{| class="wikitable alternance droite" |{{ill|Yang Earth Dragon|ja|戊辰|zh|戊辰|ko|무진|fr|Dragon de terre|de|Erde-Drache|en|Earth Dragon|lt=戊辰 (Yang Earth Dragon)|lt_ko=무진|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Earth Tiger|ja|戊寅|zh|戊寅|ko|무인|fr|Tigre de terre|de|Erde-Tiger|en|Earth Tiger|lt=戊寅 (Yang Earth Tiger)|lt_ko=무인|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Earth Rat|ja|戊子|zh|戊子|ko|무자|fr|Rat de terre|de|Erde-Ratte|en|Earth Rat|lt=戊子 (Yang Earth Rat)|lt_ko=무자|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Earth Dog|ja|戊戌|zh|戊戌|ko|무술 (간지)|fr|Chien de terre|de|Erde-Hund|en|Earth Dog|lt=戊戌 (Yang Earth Dog)|lt_ko=무술|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Earth Monkey|ja|戊申|zh|戊申|ko|무신|fr|Singe de terre|de|Erde-Affe|en|Earth Monkey|lt=戊申 (Yang Earth Monkey)|lt_ko=무신|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Earth Horse|ja|戊午|zh|戊午|ko|무오|fr|Cheval de terre|de|Erde-Pferd|en|Earth Horse|lt=戊午 (Yang Earth Horse)|lt_ko=무오|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |} == See Also == * [[Boshin War]] * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
