erd|en|Earth Horse|lt=戊午 (Yang Earth Horse)|lt_ko=무오|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Horse|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Horse|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Horse|qq=}} |} == See Also == * [[Boshin War]] * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
