="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Earth Horse|ja|1=Yang Earth Horse|2=ja|戊午|zh|1=Yang Earth Horse|2=ja|戊午|ko|무오|fr|Cheval de terre|de|Erde-Pferd|en|Earth Horse|lt=戊午 (Yang Earth Horse)|lt_ko=무오|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Horse|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Horse|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Horse|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |} == See Also == * [[:en:Boshin War|Boshin War]] * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
